## Completeness Checklist
- [ ] All AI requirements have numeric acceptance thresholds (not qualitative)
- [ ] Fallback behaviour documented per requirement
- [ ] Test dataset described with source, record count, and class distribution
- [ ] Model constraints defined (latency, memory, interpretability)
- [ ] Drift monitoring approach stated with concrete retraining trigger
- [ ] Privacy constraints on training data addressed
- [ ] Reviewed and approved by Tech Lead

## Handover Readiness
<!-- Confirms this artefact is ready for inclusion in RTM and Gate B pack. -->
- [ ] AI requirements traceable to business requirements in Business Requirements Set
- [ ] Acceptance thresholds aligned with stakeholder expectations
- [ ] Data availability confirmed or data acquisition plan in place
- [ ] Document version controlled and stored in the project artefact repository
